PN,42701
SC,0001
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F427A1774868573
OL,3,C#100m government package to restart UK
OL,4,CCO2 production site on Teesside
OL,6,FThe UK's only large-scale carbon
OL,7,Fdioxide plant is being prepared to
OL,8,Frestart its operations after the
OL,9,FGovernment agreed a #100 million
OL,10,Ffinancial support package amid fears
OL,11,Fof shortages linked to the Iran war.
OL,13,FProduction at Ensus UK's plant on
OL,14,FTeesside, which made CO2 as a by-
OL,15,Fproduct of bioethanol manufacturing,
OL,16,Fwas halted last September amid a
OL,17,Fcrisis in the UK bioethanol industry
OL,18,Fin the wake of a trade deal with the
OL,19,FUnited States.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G1/10
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
