OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,428,420,120,260,000,100
PN,42702
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F427A1774868573
OL,3,C#100m government package to restart UK
OL,4,CCO2 production site on Teesside
OL,6,FEnsus UK has now signed an agreement
OL,7,Fwith the Government to bring the
OL,8,Fmothballed plant back into operation
OL,9,Ffor a three-month period.
OL,11,FThe firm said the #100 million package
OL,12,Fhas been agreed for the plant to
OL,13,Fremain on standby and ready to start
OL,14,Fup as required.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G2/10
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,428,420,120,260,000,100
PN,42703
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F427A1774868573
OL,3,C#100m government package to restart UK
OL,4,CCO2 production site on Teesside
OL,6,FThe facility at the Wilton
OL,7,FInternational industrial site near
OL,8,FRedcar, is the UK's last remaining
OL,9,Fmajor industrial manufacturer of
OL,10,Fbiogenic carbon dioxide, which is
OL,11,Fcrucial in a wide range of sectors,
OL,12,Fincluding in the drinks and nuclear
OL,13,Findustries.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G3/10
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,428,420,120,260,000,100
PN,42704
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F427A1774868573
OL,3,C#100m government package to restart UK
OL,4,CCO2 production site on Teesside
OL,6,FThe Department for Business and Trade
OL,7,F(DBT) said the Government has taken
OL,8,Fthe decision to back the restart of
OL,9,Factivity at Ensus to "safeguard
OL,10,Fcritical national infrastructure"
OL,11,Fgiven the potential impact of a
OL,12,Fshortage on essential UK sectors,
OL,13,Fincluding healthcare, nuclear and food
OL,14,Fand drink production.
OL,16,FThe DBT said the UK risks CO2
OL,17,Fshortages due to factors including
OL,18,Fdisruptions to European fertiliser
OL,19,Fproduction and rising gas prices
OL,20,Fdriven by the Iran conflict.
OL,26,@qD@VOUrD@aO]
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G4/10
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
