OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,428,420,120,260,000,100
PN,42705
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F427A1774868573
OL,3,C#100m government package to restart UK
OL,4,CCO2 production site on Teesside
OL,6,FIt said the plant will operate for a
OL,7,Fthree-month period, which the
OL,8,Fdepartment said will bolster domestic
OL,9,FCO2 production significantly,
OL,10,Fproviding more resilience to essential
OL,11,Fsectors.
OL,13,FThe plant had been due to close
OL,14,Fpermanently in the autumn but the
OL,15,FGovernment intervened to keep it on
OL,16,Fstandby, the DBT said.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G5/10
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
