OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,428,420,120,260,000,100
PN,42706
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F427A1774868573
OL,3,C#100m government package to restart UK
OL,4,CCO2 production site on Teesside
OL,6,FEnsus UK chairman Grant Pearson said:
OL,7,F"This agreement of support from the UK
OL,8,FGovernment is excellent news for our
OL,9,Femployees and those in our extensive
OL,10,Fsupply chain.
OL,12,F"It strengthens the broader Teesside
OL,13,Fmanufacturing economy and the UK's
OL,14,Fresilience in relation to biogenic CO2
OL,15,Fsupplies.
OL,17,F"These are vital to food and drinks
OL,18,Fcompanies, as well as being important
OL,19,Fto hospitals, abattoirs and the
OL,20,Fnuclear industry."
OL,26,@oD@AOUtD@AOUyD@AOU|D@RO]
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G6/10
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,428,420,120,260,000,100
PN,42707
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F427A1774868573
OL,3,C#100m government package to restart UK
OL,4,CCO2 production site on Teesside
OL,6,FMr Pearson said: "We hope to have the
OL,7,Fplant back in full operation soon.
OL,9,F"This deal will also be very
OL,10,Fsupportive to the UK agricultural and
OL,11,Ffuel markets, including for the future
OL,12,Fexpansion which is required in more
OL,13,Fsustainable aviation and maritime
OL,14,Ffuels and in the development of
OL,15,Fgreener chemicals."
OL,26,@nD@ROUqD@AOUwD@SO]
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G7/10
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
