OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,428,420,120,260,000,100
PN,42708
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F427A1774868573
OL,3,C#100m government package to restart UK
OL,4,CCO2 production site on Teesside
OL,6,FBusiness Secretary Peter Kyle said:
OL,7,F"As a government of action we will
OL,8,Falways do what's needed to ensure
OL,9,Fresilience and protect British
OL,10,Fbusinesses from the worst impacts of
OL,11,Fglobal uncertainty.
OL,13,F"That's why we have been in
OL,14,Fdiscussions with Ensus since September
OL,15,Fto keep this critical plant on standby
OL,16,Ffor situations like this.
OL,26,@oD@AOUuD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G8/10
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
