OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,428,420,120,260,000,100
PN,42709
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F427A1774868573
OL,3,C#100m government package to restart UK
OL,4,CCO2 production site on Teesside
OL,6,F"By restarting this plant we've acted
OL,7,Fswiftly to boost the resilience of our
OL,8,Fsupply chains and protect critical UK
OL,9,Fsectors like food production, water
OL,10,Fand healthcare, as well as the jobs
OL,11,Fand communities that depend on these
OL,12,Findustries."
OL,14,FThe Teesside plant employs around 100
OL,15,Fpeople and the firm said it supports a
OL,16,Ffurther 3,000 in the UK supply chain.
OL,18,FThe facility was mothballed last year
OL,19,Ffollowing the end of a 19% tariff on
OL,20,FAmerican bioethanol imports as part of
OL,21,Fthe UK-US trade deal.
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@LO]
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G9/10
